Again; Reſolve thus; 
                  I am to Die; Therefore I will Reſign my ſelf up unto the Spirit of the Lord, that all my Enmity to God may be ſubdued; that I may Fear GOD, and Prize CHRIST, and Hate SIN, and Perfect Holineſs in the Fear of God; that the Image of Satan may be Extirpated out of my Soul, and the Holy Image of the LORD Introduced, which may render me Meet for the


Inheritance of the Saints in Light.
